cx must not implement real covert tracking, raw MAC exfiltration, law-enforcement access, carrier integration, or ingestible-device logic.

cx should build the safe foundation:

- local mock snapshots
- BLE/network/location abstractions
- consent/permissions UI
- emergency case placeholder
- audit/retention model

After implementation, cx should run available checks and report using the agent update format above.

